This is a simple jQuery plugin which allows to create a country selector in your web page.
Each option is shown as a 16x16 sized clickable flag image.
Please find detailed example in the sample.html file.

NuGet package available here: https://nuget.org/packages/jQuery.countrySelector/
Sourceforge homepage: https://sourceforge.net/p/jquerycountryse/
Github homepage: https://github.com/kylinwater/jQuery-Country-Selector/

For any question please contact jia.kang.1982@gmail.com
